00:16:35.140 --> 00:16:38.300
And what is the risk of having this in production?

00:16:38.480 --> 00:16:45.340
Because maybe if it's a system that contains a lot of bias or we cannot control this bias,

00:16:46.020 --> 00:16:49.260
maybe it's better to go for other kind of options.

00:16:50.340 --> 00:16:51.540
That is my point of view.

